{
  "book": "1nephi",
  "bookName": "1 Nephi",
  "chapter": 8,
  "voice": {
    "provider": "elevenlabs",
    "voice_id": "ddDFRErfhdc2asyySOG5",
    "model_id": "eleven_multilingual_v2",
    "settings": {
      "stability": 0.5,
      "similarity_boost": 0.75,
      "style": 0.35,
      "use_speaker_boost": true
    },
    "name": "Samuel"
  },
  "pauses": {
    "line_ms": 180,
    "verse_ms": 500
  },
  "duration": 443.754,
  "lines": [
    {
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 3.251,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that we had gathered together",
      "verse": "8:1",
      "lineIndex": 0
    },
    {
      "start": 3.431,
      "end": 7.518,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "all manner of seeds of every kind, both of grain of every kind,",
      "verse": "8:1",
      "lineIndex": 1
    },
    {
      "start": 7.698,
      "end": 10.67,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also of the seeds of fruit of every kind.",
      "verse": "8:1",
      "lineIndex": 2
    },
    {
      "start": 11.35,
      "end": 16.18,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that while my father tarried in the wilderness",
      "verse": "8:2",
      "lineIndex": 4
    },
    {
      "start": 16.36,
      "end": 18.032,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "he spake unto us, saying:",
      "verse": "8:2",
      "lineIndex": 5
    },
    {
      "start": 18.212,
      "end": 20.302,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Behold, I have dreamed a dream;",
      "verse": "8:2",
      "lineIndex": 6
    },
    {
      "start": 20.482,
      "end": 23.268,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "or, in other words, I have seen a vision.",
      "verse": "8:2",
      "lineIndex": 7
    },
    {
      "start": 23.948,
      "end": 27.524,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And behold, because of the thing which I have seen,",
      "verse": "8:3",
      "lineIndex": 8
    },
    {
      "start": 27.704,
      "end": 30.119,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I have reason to rejoice in the Lord,",
      "verse": "8:3",
      "lineIndex": 9
    },
    {
      "start": 30.299,
      "end": 32.946,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "because of Nephi and also of Sam;",
      "verse": "8:3",
      "lineIndex": 10
    },
    {
      "start": 33.126,
      "end": 35.123,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for I have reason to suppose",
      "verse": "8:3",
      "lineIndex": 11
    },
    {
      "start": 35.303,
      "end": 36.418,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that they,",
      "verse": "8:3",
      "lineIndex": 12
    },
    {
      "start": 36.598,
      "end": 38.734,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also many of their seed,",
      "verse": "8:3",
      "lineIndex": 13
    },
    {
      "start": 38.914,
      "end": 40.214,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "will be saved.",
      "verse": "8:3",
      "lineIndex": 14
    },
    {
      "start": 40.894,
      "end": 43.03,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "But behold, Laman and Lemuel,",
      "verse": "8:4",
      "lineIndex": 15
    },
    {
      "start": 43.21,
      "end": 45.625,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I fear exceedingly because of you;",
      "verse": "8:4",
      "lineIndex": 16
    },
    {
      "start": 45.805,
      "end": 48.499,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for behold, methought I saw in my dream,",
      "verse": "8:4",
      "lineIndex": 17
    },
    {
      "start": 48.679,
      "end": 51.094,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "a dark and dreary wilderness.",
      "verse": "8:4",
      "lineIndex": 18
    },
    {
      "start": 51.774,
      "end": 54.142,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that I saw a man,",
      "verse": "8:5",
      "lineIndex": 19
    },
    {
      "start": 54.322,
      "end": 56.365,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and he was dressed in a white robe;",
      "verse": "8:5",
      "lineIndex": 20
    },
    {
      "start": 56.545,
      "end": 58.356,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and he came and stood before me.",
      "verse": "8:5",
      "lineIndex": 21
    },
    {
      "start": 59.036,
      "end": 61.544,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that he spake unto me,",
      "verse": "8:6",
      "lineIndex": 22
    },
    {
      "start": 61.724,
      "end": 63.349,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and bade me follow him.",
      "verse": "8:6",
      "lineIndex": 23
    },
    {
      "start": 64.029,
      "end": 66.815,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that as I followed him",
      "verse": "8:7",
      "lineIndex": 24
    },
    {
      "start": 66.995,
      "end": 70.478,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I beheld myself that I was in a dark and dreary waste.",
      "verse": "8:7",
      "lineIndex": 25
    },
    {
      "start": 71.158,
      "end": 75.523,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And after I had traveled for the space of many hours in darkness,",
      "verse": "8:8",
      "lineIndex": 26
    },
    {
      "start": 75.703,
      "end": 77.793,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I began to pray unto the Lord",
      "verse": "8:8",
      "lineIndex": 27
    },
    {
      "start": 77.973,
      "end": 79.784,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that he would have mercy on me,",
      "verse": "8:8",
      "lineIndex": 28
    },
    {
      "start": 79.964,
      "end": 83.586,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "according to the multitude of his tender mercies.",
      "verse": "8:8",
      "lineIndex": 29
    },
    {
      "start": 84.266,
      "end": 87.47,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass after I had prayed unto the Lord",
      "verse": "8:9",
      "lineIndex": 30
    },
    {
      "start": 87.65,
      "end": 90.297,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I beheld a large and spacious field.",
      "verse": "8:9",
      "lineIndex": 31
    },
    {
      "start": 90.977,
      "end": 93.717,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that I beheld a tree,",
      "verse": "8:10",
      "lineIndex": 32
    },
    {
      "start": 93.897,
      "end": 96.683,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "whose fruit was desirable to make one happy.",
      "verse": "8:10",
      "lineIndex": 33
    },
    {
      "start": 97.363,
      "end": 99.871,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that I did go forth",
      "verse": "8:11",
      "lineIndex": 34
    },
    {
      "start": 100.051,
      "end": 102.28,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and partake of the fruit thereof;",
      "verse": "8:11",
      "lineIndex": 35
    },
    {
      "start": 102.46,
      "end": 105.061,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I beheld that it was most sweet,",
      "verse": "8:11",
      "lineIndex": 36
    },
    {
      "start": 105.241,
      "end": 107.842,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "above all that I ever before tasted.",
      "verse": "8:11",
      "lineIndex": 37
    },
    {
      "start": 108.022,
      "end": 111.644,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Yea, and I beheld that the fruit thereof was white,",
      "verse": "8:11",
      "lineIndex": 38
    },
    {
      "start": 111.824,
      "end": 115.4,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "to exceed all the whiteness that I had ever seen.",
      "verse": "8:11",
      "lineIndex": 39
    },
    {
      "start": 116.08,
      "end": 118.216,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And as I partook of the fruit thereof",
      "verse": "8:12",
      "lineIndex": 40
    },
    {
      "start": 118.396,
      "end": 121.182,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "it filled my soul with exceedingly great joy;",
      "verse": "8:12",
      "lineIndex": 41
    },
    {
      "start": 121.362,
      "end": 123.916,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "wherefore, I began to be desirous",
      "verse": "8:12",
      "lineIndex": 42
    },
    {
      "start": 124.096,
      "end": 126.79,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that my family should partake of it also;",
      "verse": "8:12",
      "lineIndex": 43
    },
    {
      "start": 126.97,
      "end": 130.499,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for I knew that it was desirable above all other fruit.",
      "verse": "8:12",
      "lineIndex": 44
    },
    {
      "start": 131.179,
      "end": 133.408,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And as I cast my eyes round about,",
      "verse": "8:13",
      "lineIndex": 45
    },
    {
      "start": 133.588,
      "end": 136.467,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that perhaps I might discover my family also,",
      "verse": "8:13",
      "lineIndex": 46
    },
    {
      "start": 136.647,
      "end": 138.783,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I beheld a river of water;",
      "verse": "8:13",
      "lineIndex": 47
    },
    {
      "start": 138.963,
      "end": 140.449,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and it ran along,",
      "verse": "8:13",
      "lineIndex": 48
    },
    {
      "start": 140.629,
      "end": 142.208,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and it was near the tree",
      "verse": "8:13",
      "lineIndex": 49
    },
    {
      "start": 142.388,
      "end": 144.756,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "of which I was partaking the fruit.",
      "verse": "8:13",
      "lineIndex": 50
    },
    {
      "start": 145.436,
      "end": 148.037,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I looked to behold from whence it came;",
      "verse": "8:14",
      "lineIndex": 52
    },
    {
      "start": 148.217,
      "end": 151.282,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I saw the head thereof a little way off;",
      "verse": "8:14",
      "lineIndex": 53
    },
    {
      "start": 151.462,
      "end": 154.806,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and at the head thereof I beheld your mother Sariah,",
      "verse": "8:14",
      "lineIndex": 54
    },
    {
      "start": 154.986,
      "end": 156.751,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and Sam, and Nephi;",
      "verse": "8:14",
      "lineIndex": 55
    },
    {
      "start": 156.931,
      "end": 160.414,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and they stood as if they knew not whither they should go.",
      "verse": "8:14",
      "lineIndex": 56
    },
    {
      "start": 161.094,
      "end": 164.205,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that I beckoned unto them;",
      "verse": "8:15",
      "lineIndex": 57
    },
    {
      "start": 164.385,
      "end": 167.404,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I also did say unto them with a loud voice",
      "verse": "8:15",
      "lineIndex": 58
    },
    {
      "start": 167.584,
      "end": 169.442,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that they should come unto me,",
      "verse": "8:15",
      "lineIndex": 59
    },
    {
      "start": 169.622,
      "end": 171.34,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and partake of the fruit,",
      "verse": "8:15",
      "lineIndex": 60
    },
    {
      "start": 171.52,
      "end": 174.306,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which was desirable above all other fruit.",
      "verse": "8:15",
      "lineIndex": 61
    },
    {
      "start": 174.986,
      "end": 177.958,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that they did come unto me",
      "verse": "8:16",
      "lineIndex": 62
    },
    {
      "start": 178.138,
      "end": 180.414,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and partake of the fruit also.",
      "verse": "8:16",
      "lineIndex": 63
    },
    {
      "start": 181.094,
      "end": 186.527,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that I was desirous that Laman and Lemuel should come",
      "verse": "8:17",
      "lineIndex": 64
    },
    {
      "start": 186.707,
      "end": 188.89,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and partake of the fruit also;",
      "verse": "8:17",
      "lineIndex": 65
    },
    {
      "start": 189.07,
      "end": 191.206,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "wherefore, I cast mine eyes",
      "verse": "8:17",
      "lineIndex": 66
    },
    {
      "start": 191.386,
      "end": 193.708,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "towards the head of the river,",
      "verse": "8:17",
      "lineIndex": 67
    },
    {
      "start": 193.888,
      "end": 196.349,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that perhaps I might see them.",
      "verse": "8:17",
      "lineIndex": 68
    },
    {
      "start": 197.029,
      "end": 199.676,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that I saw them,",
      "verse": "8:18",
      "lineIndex": 69
    },
    {
      "start": 199.856,
      "end": 202.132,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "but they would not come unto me",
      "verse": "8:18",
      "lineIndex": 70
    },
    {
      "start": 202.312,
      "end": 203.891,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and partake of the fruit.",
      "verse": "8:18",
      "lineIndex": 71
    },
    {
      "start": 204.571,
      "end": 206.707,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I beheld a rod of iron,",
      "verse": "8:19",
      "lineIndex": 72
    },
    {
      "start": 206.887,
      "end": 209.534,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and it extended along the bank of the river,",
      "verse": "8:19",
      "lineIndex": 73
    },
    {
      "start": 209.714,
      "end": 212.268,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and led to the tree by which I stood.",
      "verse": "8:19",
      "lineIndex": 74
    },
    {
      "start": 212.948,
      "end": 216.199,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I also beheld a strait and narrow path,",
      "verse": "8:20",
      "lineIndex": 75
    },
    {
      "start": 216.379,
      "end": 218.933,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which came along by the rod of iron,",
      "verse": "8:20",
      "lineIndex": 76
    },
    {
      "start": 219.113,
      "end": 221.342,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "even to the tree by which I stood;",
      "verse": "8:20",
      "lineIndex": 77
    },
    {
      "start": 221.522,
      "end": 224.726,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and it also led by the head of the fountain,",
      "verse": "8:20",
      "lineIndex": 78
    },
    {
      "start": 224.906,
      "end": 228.714,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "unto a large and spacious field, as if it had been a world.",
      "verse": "8:20",
      "lineIndex": 79
    },
    {
      "start": 229.394,
      "end": 232.134,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I saw numberless concourses of people,",
      "verse": "8:21",
      "lineIndex": 80
    },
    {
      "start": 232.314,
      "end": 234.59,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "many of whom were pressing forward,",
      "verse": "8:21",
      "lineIndex": 81
    },
    {
      "start": 234.77,
      "end": 237.649,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that they might obtain the path",
      "verse": "8:21",
      "lineIndex": 82
    },
    {
      "start": 237.829,
      "end": 240.383,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which led unto the tree by which I stood.",
      "verse": "8:21",
      "lineIndex": 83
    },
    {
      "start": 241.063,
      "end": 243.896,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that they did come forth,",
      "verse": "8:22",
      "lineIndex": 85
    },
    {
      "start": 244.076,
      "end": 247.048,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and commence in the path which led to the tree.",
      "verse": "8:22",
      "lineIndex": 86
    },
    {
      "start": 247.728,
      "end": 251.257,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that there arose a mist of darkness;",
      "verse": "8:23",
      "lineIndex": 87
    },
    {
      "start": 251.437,
      "end": 254.734,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yea, even a exceedingly great mist of darkness,",
      "verse": "8:23",
      "lineIndex": 88
    },
    {
      "start": 254.914,
      "end": 259.14,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "insomuch that they who had commenced in the path did lose their way,",
      "verse": "8:23",
      "lineIndex": 89
    },
    {
      "start": 259.32,
      "end": 261.828,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that they wandered off and were lost.",
      "verse": "8:23",
      "lineIndex": 90
    },
    {
      "start": 262.508,
      "end": 265.945,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that I beheld others pressing forward,",
      "verse": "8:24",
      "lineIndex": 91
    },
    {
      "start": 266.125,
      "end": 270.49,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and they came forth and caught hold of the end of the rod of iron;",
      "verse": "8:24",
      "lineIndex": 92
    },
    {
      "start": 270.67,
      "end": 273.874,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and they did press forward through the mist of darkness,",
      "verse": "8:24",
      "lineIndex": 93
    },
    {
      "start": 274.054,
      "end": 276.004,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "clinging to the rod of iron,",
      "verse": "8:24",
      "lineIndex": 94
    },
    {
      "start": 276.184,
      "end": 278.274,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "even until they did come forth",
      "verse": "8:24",
      "lineIndex": 95
    },
    {
      "start": 278.454,
      "end": 280.59,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and partake of the fruit of the tree.",
      "verse": "8:24",
      "lineIndex": 96
    },
    {
      "start": 281.27,
      "end": 284.196,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And after they had partaken of the fruit of the tree",
      "verse": "8:25",
      "lineIndex": 97
    },
    {
      "start": 284.376,
      "end": 287.441,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "they did cast their eyes about as if they were ashamed.",
      "verse": "8:25",
      "lineIndex": 98
    },
    {
      "start": 288.121,
      "end": 290.629,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I also cast my eyes round about,",
      "verse": "8:26",
      "lineIndex": 100
    },
    {
      "start": 290.809,
      "end": 294.664,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and beheld, on the other side of the river of water,",
      "verse": "8:26",
      "lineIndex": 101
    },
    {
      "start": 294.844,
      "end": 297.027,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "a great and spacious building;",
      "verse": "8:26",
      "lineIndex": 102
    },
    {
      "start": 297.207,
      "end": 299.25,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and it stood as it were in the air,",
      "verse": "8:26",
      "lineIndex": 103
    },
    {
      "start": 299.43,
      "end": 301.148,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "high above the earth.",
      "verse": "8:26",
      "lineIndex": 104
    },
    {
      "start": 301.828,
      "end": 303.546,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it was filled with people,",
      "verse": "8:27",
      "lineIndex": 105
    },
    {
      "start": 303.726,
      "end": 305.491,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "both old and young,",
      "verse": "8:27",
      "lineIndex": 106
    },
    {
      "start": 305.671,
      "end": 307.389,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "both male and female;",
      "verse": "8:27",
      "lineIndex": 107
    },
    {
      "start": 307.569,
      "end": 310.495,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and their manner of dress was exceedingly fine;",
      "verse": "8:27",
      "lineIndex": 108
    },
    {
      "start": 310.675,
      "end": 314.204,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and they were in the attitude of mocking and pointing their fingers",
      "verse": "8:27",
      "lineIndex": 109
    },
    {
      "start": 314.384,
      "end": 318.285,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "towards those who had come at and were partaking of the fruit.",
      "verse": "8:27",
      "lineIndex": 110
    },
    {
      "start": 318.965,
      "end": 322.076,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And after they had tasted of the fruit they were ashamed,",
      "verse": "8:28",
      "lineIndex": 111
    },
    {
      "start": 322.256,
      "end": 324.764,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "because of those that were scoffing at them;",
      "verse": "8:28",
      "lineIndex": 112
    },
    {
      "start": 324.944,
      "end": 328.52,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and they fell away into forbidden paths and were lost.",
      "verse": "8:28",
      "lineIndex": 113
    },
    {
      "start": 329.2,
      "end": 332.962,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And now I, Nephi, do not speak all the words of my father.",
      "verse": "8:29",
      "lineIndex": 114
    },
    {
      "start": 333.642,
      "end": 335.732,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "But, to be short in writing,",
      "verse": "8:30",
      "lineIndex": 115
    },
    {
      "start": 335.912,
      "end": 339.302,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "behold, he saw other multitudes pressing forward;",
      "verse": "8:30",
      "lineIndex": 116
    },
    {
      "start": 339.482,
      "end": 343.104,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and they came and caught hold of the end of the rod of iron;",
      "verse": "8:30",
      "lineIndex": 117
    },
    {
      "start": 343.284,
      "end": 345.606,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and they did press their way forward,",
      "verse": "8:30",
      "lineIndex": 118
    },
    {
      "start": 345.786,
      "end": 348.805,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "continually holding fast to the rod of iron,",
      "verse": "8:30",
      "lineIndex": 119
    },
    {
      "start": 348.985,
      "end": 351.168,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "until they came forth and fell down",
      "verse": "8:30",
      "lineIndex": 120
    },
    {
      "start": 351.348,
      "end": 353.809,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and partook of the fruit of the tree.",
      "verse": "8:30",
      "lineIndex": 121
    },
    {
      "start": 354.489,
      "end": 356.672,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And he also saw other multitudes",
      "verse": "8:31",
      "lineIndex": 122
    },
    {
      "start": 356.852,
      "end": 360.474,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "feeling their way towards that great and spacious building.",
      "verse": "8:31",
      "lineIndex": 123
    },
    {
      "start": 361.154,
      "end": 365.705,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that many were drowned in the depths of the fountain;",
      "verse": "8:32",
      "lineIndex": 124
    },
    {
      "start": 365.885,
      "end": 369.74,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and many were lost from his view, wandering in strange roads.",
      "verse": "8:32",
      "lineIndex": 125
    },
    {
      "start": 370.42,
      "end": 372.231,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And great was the multitude",
      "verse": "8:33",
      "lineIndex": 126
    },
    {
      "start": 372.411,
      "end": 375.012,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that did enter into that strange building.",
      "verse": "8:33",
      "lineIndex": 127
    },
    {
      "start": 375.192,
      "end": 377.978,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And after they did enter into that building",
      "verse": "8:33",
      "lineIndex": 128
    },
    {
      "start": 378.158,
      "end": 380.666,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "they did point the finger of scorn at me",
      "verse": "8:33",
      "lineIndex": 129
    },
    {
      "start": 380.846,
      "end": 383.772,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and those that were partaking of the fruit also;",
      "verse": "8:33",
      "lineIndex": 130
    },
    {
      "start": 383.952,
      "end": 385.485,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "but we heeded them not.",
      "verse": "8:33",
      "lineIndex": 131
    },
    {
      "start": 386.165,
      "end": 388.115,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "These are the words of my father:",
      "verse": "8:34",
      "lineIndex": 132
    },
    {
      "start": 388.295,
      "end": 391.406,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "For as many as heeded them, had fallen away.",
      "verse": "8:34",
      "lineIndex": 133
    },
    {
      "start": 392.086,
      "end": 396.033,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And Laman and Lemuel partook not of the fruit, said my father.",
      "verse": "8:35",
      "lineIndex": 134
    },
    {
      "start": 396.713,
      "end": 399.546,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass after my father had spoken",
      "verse": "8:36",
      "lineIndex": 136
    },
    {
      "start": 399.726,
      "end": 402.002,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "all the words of his dream or vision,",
      "verse": "8:36",
      "lineIndex": 137
    },
    {
      "start": 402.182,
      "end": 403.715,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which were many,",
      "verse": "8:36",
      "lineIndex": 138
    },
    {
      "start": 403.895,
      "end": 408.028,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "he said unto us, because of these things which he saw in a vision,",
      "verse": "8:36",
      "lineIndex": 139
    },
    {
      "start": 408.208,
      "end": 410.994,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "he exceedingly feared for Laman and Lemuel;",
      "verse": "8:36",
      "lineIndex": 140
    },
    {
      "start": 411.174,
      "end": 415.679,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yea, he feared lest they should be cast off from the presence of the Lord.",
      "verse": "8:36",
      "lineIndex": 141
    },
    {
      "start": 416.359,
      "end": 418.402,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And he did exhort them then",
      "verse": "8:37",
      "lineIndex": 142
    },
    {
      "start": 418.582,
      "end": 421.09,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "with all the feeling of a tender parent,",
      "verse": "8:37",
      "lineIndex": 143
    },
    {
      "start": 421.27,
      "end": 423.453,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that they would hearken to his words,",
      "verse": "8:37",
      "lineIndex": 144
    },
    {
      "start": 423.633,
      "end": 426.559,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that perhaps the Lord would be merciful to them,",
      "verse": "8:37",
      "lineIndex": 145
    },
    {
      "start": 426.739,
      "end": 428.225,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and not cast them off;",
      "verse": "8:37",
      "lineIndex": 146
    },
    {
      "start": 428.405,
      "end": 430.541,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yea, my father did preach unto them.",
      "verse": "8:37",
      "lineIndex": 147
    },
    {
      "start": 431.221,
      "end": 433.729,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And after he had preached unto them,",
      "verse": "8:38",
      "lineIndex": 148
    },
    {
      "start": 433.909,
      "end": 437.253,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also prophesied unto them of many things,",
      "verse": "8:38",
      "lineIndex": 149
    },
    {
      "start": 437.433,
      "end": 440.544,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "he bade them to keep the commandments of the Lord;",
      "verse": "8:38",
      "lineIndex": 150
    },
    {
      "start": 440.724,
      "end": 443.092,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and he did cease speaking unto them.",
      "verse": "8:38",
      "lineIndex": 151
    }
  ]
}